ary&timestamp=153.0)\n  - [Scrunch analysis tool provides aggregate data on AI citations, including average positioning, competitor comparisons, and opportunities](https://fathom.video/share/XAEFkPMptVVtL83VwgCNbgs4okka4taY?tab=summary&timestamp=153.0)\n  - [Data likely pulled from GA4, but needs verification with data team](https://fathom.video/share/XAEFkPMptVVtL83VwgCNbgs4okka4taY?tab=summary&timestamp=205.0)\n\n### Vendor Page Strategy\n\n  - [Exploring adding more vendor-related pages, potentially focused on pricing queries](https://fathom.video/share/XAEFkPMptVVtL83VwgCNbgs4okka4taY?tab=summary&timestamp=300.0)\n  - [\"Versus\" pages getting cited more in AI overviews](https://fathom.video/share/XAEFkPMptVVtL83VwgCNbgs4okka4taY?tab=summary&timestamp=333.0)\n  - [Current content format (direct answers, charts) performing well for AI citations](https://fathom.video/share/XAEFkPMptVVtL83VwgCNbgs4okka4taY?tab=summary&timestamp=348.0)\n  - [Potential to expand content on vendor overview page](https://fathom.video/share/XAEFkPMptVVtL83VwgCNbgs4okka4taY?tab=summary&timestamp=348.0)\n\n## Next Steps\n\n  - [Mara to follow up with Loom video on full Looker report data (currently showing error)](https://fathom.video/share/XAEFkPMptVVtL83VwgCNbgs4okka4taY?tab=summary&timestamp=62.0)\n  - [Investigate potential for expanding vendor overview page content](https://fathom.video/share/XAEFkPMptVVtL83VwgCNbgs4okka4taY?tab=summary&timestamp=415.0)\n  - [Consider setting up Scrunch for more granular AI citation data](https://fathom.video/share/XAEFkPMptVVtL83VwgCNbgs4okka4taY?tab=summary&timestamp=198.0)\n  - [Discuss vendor page expansion strategies in next week's meeting](https://fathom.video/share/XAEFkPMptVVtL83VwgCNbgs4okka4taY?tab=summary&timestamp=420.0)\n"
